Hello everyone this is my first source/client coded using deltascape! I've coded everything and added everything everyone on the server who joined said that they could code ofcourse gave them chances and they failed. so i added and coded everything! crafting goes to garboscape source i've gotten that to work from garboscape so they get creds for crafting and deltascape gets creds for the base! (sorry not alot of pics) AND ANTI SYIPKER! skillz [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/skillz.jpg[/img] Mining [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/mine.jpg[/img] Home/Shops (they are coded really well..) [img]http://i257.photobucket.com/albums/hh219/brendagriffiths_2008/home-1.jpg[/img]
Well i hope you'll enjoy this source Version2 will come soon with new godsword stances etc. More updated!
Client download:http://www.megaupload.com/?d=3WXFYV48 Server download:http://www.megaupload.com/?d=OM4TBU6Y
This is my first source.. i dont want any flaming plz i worked my hardest. i added dragon claws special etc. and the right gfx ids i hope you all enjoy. and please comment if u download and make sure u give me garboscape and deltascape creds. *garboscape for crafting and arrangement of portals and shops arrangement at home..(was very neat)* *deltascape for the source base* *me for coding/programming the server and client* thanks everyone. enjoy ANYONE LOOKING FOR a coder just pm me and tell me. (also if thats against the rules just let me know ill remove.)
ALREADY CAUGHT ONE LEECHER CALLED KYLE OWNZ WHO OWNZ PKLOCUS! ONE MORE CATCH AND ITS GOING DOWN!
